# 🏦 Loan Management System

## 📌 Overview

The Loan Management System is a Python-based application developed to automate loan record management using Excel, MySQL, and Python.

The application reads loan records from Excel, cleans and validates the data, stores it in a MySQL database, performs business analytics, generates charts, and exports Excel reports.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Read loan data from Excel
- Clean and validate records
- Store records in MySQL
- Perform loan analytics
- Generate bar charts
- Generate Excel reports
- Execute the complete workflow using one command

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- Python 3
- Pandas
- MySQL
- MySQL Connector
- Matplotlib
- OpenPyXL
- VS Code

